    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Seriously, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight! I\u2019ve babied this thing from day one, keeping it garage-kept and professionally detailed. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
