    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the entire rev range. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term structural and mechanical integrity. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, with the suspension geometry remaining perfectly aligned. The exterior finish and Nappa leather interior are devoid of any imperfections, reflecting a vehicle that has been maintained to a concours standard without deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
